knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺度擺低哂我地平台link<br />\n<br />\n香港良心Guide (網頁+IG):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.leungsumshops.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.leungsumshops.com%2F&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=3f0962b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.leungsumshops.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkshoplist/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkshoplist%2F&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=ae88bd88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkshoplist/</a><br />\n<br />\n全民罷買日 Byebuyday (IG):<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/byebuydayhk?igshid=110rffoj3s8vs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fbyebuydayhk%3Figshid%3D110rffoj3s8vs&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=270ad101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/byebuydayhk?igshid=110rffoj3s8vs</a><br />\n<br />\n黃業 (Telegram bot):<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ybshopbot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fybshopbot&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=d5a4d8ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ybshopbot</a><br />\n<br />\nRestarthk (整合網):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.restart-hk.com/ShopList.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.restart-hk.com%2FShopList.html&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=a701257a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.restart-hk.com/ShopList.html</a><br />\n<br />\n終極黃藍地圖 (地圖):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/edit?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fedit%3Fmid%3D10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=6ab92a3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/edit?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs</a><br />\n(save地圖落手機方法:<br />\n㩒上面條link &gt; 開Google Map app &gt; 左上角三橫icon &gt; 您的位置 / Your Place &gt; 地圖 / Your Map &gt; 開地圖搵食)<br />\n<br />\n終極黃藍地圖圖檔 (For文宣印刷/派傳單俾長輩):<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1ScmlrDf7eIVWLUs45nPr_2gbWK98Hkld\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1ScmlrDf7eIVWLUs45nPr_2gbWK98Hkld&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=393bec2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1ScmlrDf7eIVWLUs45nPr_2gbWK98Hkld</a><br />\n<br />\nWhatsgap (App):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/whatsgaphk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwhatsgaphk%2F&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=bb6f0ba8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/whatsgaphk/</a><br />\nApp 請到PlayStore/AppStore 下載<br />\n<br />\n良心好西foodie (食評):<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/goodwest_standwithhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fgoodwest_standwithhk&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=4bb12b5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/goodwest_standwithhk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">希望唔只爆買日，各位手足每一日都要幫襯黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"}]}